trans-unit.source: The SoapServerType class represents the type on which the XML Web service is based.
trans-unit.target: SoapServerType 類別表示 XML Web service 所依據的類型。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> on which this XML Web service is based.
A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.WebServiceProtocols"></xref> value that specifies the transmission protocols that are used to decrypt data sent in the XML Web service request.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Configuration.WebServiceProtocols"> </xref>值，指定用來解密 XML Web 服務要求中傳送的資料傳輸通訊協定。

trans-unit.source: Returns the duplicate <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref> associated with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: 傳回重複<xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref>與指定之索引鍵相關聯。

trans-unit.source: The key associated with the desired duplicate <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 想要重複項目相關聯的索引鍵<xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: The duplicate <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref> associated with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: 重複<xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref>與指定之索引鍵相關聯。

trans-unit.source: Returns the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref> associated with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: 傳回<xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref>與指定之索引鍵相關聯。

trans-unit.source: The key associated with the desired <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 想要的相關聯的索引鍵<xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod"></xref> associated with the specified key.
Returns a <xref:System.Boolean> that indicates whether SOAP data transmissions sent to and from this XML Web service are encoded by default.
trans-unit.target: 傳回<xref:System.Boolean>，表示預設是否會編碼此 XML Web service 來回傳送的 SOAP 資料傳輸。</xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if SOAP data transmissions sent to and from this XML Web service are encoded by default; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果預設值，來進行編碼的這個 XML Web service 來回傳送的 SOAP 資料傳輸否則， <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref:System.String> that contains the namespace to which this XML Web service belongs.
trans-unit.target: 取得<xref:System.String>，其中包含此 XML Web 服務所屬之命名空間。</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> that contains the namespace to which this XML Web service belongs.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.String>，其中包含此 XML Web 服務所屬之命名空間。</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref:System.Boolean> that indicates whether SOAP messages that are routed to this XML Web service are routed based on the <xref uid="langword_csharp_SOAPAction" name="SOAPAction" href=""></xref> HTTP header.
trans-unit.target: 傳回<xref:System.Boolean>，指出是否會路由傳送至這個 XML Web 服務的 SOAP 訊息會路由傳送根據<xref uid="langword_csharp_SOAPAction" name="SOAPAction" href=""> </xref> HTTP 標頭。</xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if SOAP messages that are routed to this XML Web service are routed based on the <xref uid="langword_csharp_SOAPAction" name="SOAPAction" href=""></xref> HTTP header; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果會路由傳送至這個 XML Web 服務的 SOAP 訊息都會路由傳送根據<xref uid="langword_csharp_SOAPAction" name="SOAPAction" href=""> </xref> HTTP 標頭，否則<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。
